Lux - The lightweight web framework


Examples:

---------------
import lux
lux.path("~/html")
lux.page("index",".html", 
"""
This is the index page.
""" )
lux.run(3030)

---------------


Installation:

---------------
There is no pip package for this. 

Just download the file into the directory of your project and then put this in your code:
"import lux"


Doc:

---------------

Functions:

path(directory) # The path to your html files. [optional]

page(name,type,text): # This will create a page.

run(port) # This will run the server
